Descriptions: A man was standing confrontationally behind his bike which seemed to have been hit by a woman driving a white car behind him. They appeared to be arguing or talking about the accident.

There were 3 people, a man with a knife, a man with a bag and a woman. The man was holding his knife with his right hand near his left wrist and seemed as though he was threating the other man and the woman. In between the man with a knife and two others there was a table. On the other side of the table the man with a bag seemed to be reaching for something in the bag while having a stern and calm face. The woman appeared scared and had her hands raised.
A man was by himself in a messy room standing on a makeshift stool trying to grab a bottle of cinnamon jack daniels from the top of a cubbord in his kitchen.

A person was alone in a room sitting on a couch holding a pillow and seemed as though they were going to throw it. There was a chess board on a table in front of them and a psychadelic image of a mountain on the wall the person was facing.

There were three people, a woman standing under a tree sweeping leaves. A man in a green shirt and blue hat watching her sweep. And another woman sitting down on a table watching the other woman sweep as well.
There was a man holding a pen sitting on a couch in front of a table. On the table there were several items including tape
There was a person sitting on a couch with a table in front of them. They kept their foot on the table and were holding their foot with their hands. The table had many items on it.
There was a person sitting on a couch holding a pamphlet in front of a table. On the table were many items including a britta filter and a cup full of pens
There was a person on a couch in front of a table holding a piece of paper. On the table there were many items including a Tv remote.
There was a person holding an orange and blue flannel on a couch in front of a table. On the table there was sunscreen and other items.
In the background there were two women sitting on a circular table and in front of them was a man cleaning a separate circular table.
There was a man folding clothes while on a blue couch in front of a table. On the table was a speaker and it seemed as if he was listening to music.

There was a man with long hair in a messy room that was strewn with many objects including guitars and a tennis racket. The room also had a table. The man appeared to be watching something exciting, possibly a sports game of some kind.

There were 3 people running towards a green soccer ball on a lawn. The ball was near the bottom left of the screen. Two of the people, both girls, were running towards the ball from the left to the right. A man was running towards the ball, appearing to run towards the direction that the image was taken.
There was a person on a blue couch holding a roll of tape and pulling at it as if to tear a piece off. There were several objects on the table.
There was a person holding a cloth of some kind on a bathroom sink. The sink had their phone and glasses resting on it as well as several other items.
There was a person with long hair bending over while searching for a tennis ball that had gotten to be below a chair in a room with musical instruments.
There was a person holding an object, it appeared to be a yellow master lock, and was messing with it. On the table in front of him was a book and several other objects. He was sitting on a couch.
A person was sitting on a couch holding a cup and the cap to a bottle of new amsterdam vodka. He appeared to be drinking. He was sitting in front of a table containing many objects.

There was a person sitting on a couch in front of a table. They had their hand above the table on top of a piece of paper towel as if to catch the drippings of something red that was on their right hand. The table also contained many other objects.
